title: Cubetek CUBETEK Ezcast HDMI Air Streamer Selector Box

Do all this with an Easy Downloadable APP from App store or Google Play or from www.iezvu.com with easy Upgrade of Software option. Its main feature to stream all your smart device like Mobile, Laptop, Pad content to HD TV wirelessly alongwith internet option makes it a better buy than Chromecast. Compelte Online tutorial available to connect and use your devices available. All you require is to download an App called " EZCAST" free for all Operating Systems.
